author: Cheyenne Roundtree For Dailymail.Com
title: Memes poke fun at Atlanta Falcons' Super Bowl choke | Daily Mail Online
text: 'Just like Joffrey': Hilarious memes poke fun at how Atlanta Falcons choked in the Super Bowl after losing in overtime to the New England Patriots Atlanta lost to New England during overtime in the Super Bowl on Sunday The internet quickly exploded with memes teasing the Falcon's epic choke The final score of the game was 34-28, Atlanta had a 25-point lead Social media pointed out the team's performance was similar to Game of Throne's character King Joffrey who choked and died at his 'shining moment' Published: 07:06 GMT, 6 February 2017 | Updated: 11:26 GMT, 6 February 2017 647 shares
